subdl - The Subtitles Downloader
================================

[![Build Status](
  https://travis-ci.org/andreafrancia/subdl.png)](
  https://travis-ci.org/andreafrancia/subdl)

Download the italian subtitle for your favorite show.

Usage example:

    $ subdl ~/Downloads/The.Simpsons.S24E14.HDTV.x264-LOL.mp4

Installation:

    $ gem install subdl

The application needs to access to your www.italiansubs.net account. To make 
available your credentials to `subdl` store them in the `~/.itasa-credentials` 
file using the following format:

    $ cat ~/.itasa-credentials
    username
    password


